SIMPLE: expressly
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Expressly
<hw>Ex*press"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an express manner; in
direct terms; with distinct purpose; particularly; <as>as, a book
written <ex>expressly</ex> for the young</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The word of the Lord came <qex>expressly</qex> unto Ezekiel.</q>
<rj><qau>Ezek. i. 3.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I am sent <qex>expressly</qex> to your lordship.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Expressman</ent>⟦br⟧
